{"tid":1419521,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣入]麻煩煲大荃灣民防隊同機場罷工！","createTime":"2019-08-06T01:41:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T12:56:45.000Z","uid":45788,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"cadccd2d9e53e0b2f6685aa205a4e4969853a65f","tid":1419521,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:41:51.000Z","msg":"荃灣民防隊規模唔大<br />\n<br />\n但成功將部分恐怖分子擊退<br />\n證明咗<span style=\"color: red;\">治安唔一定要黑社會搞</span><br />\n<br />\n你要獨立調查，解散警隊<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">首先要令黑社會價值得翻鎮壓示威</span><br />\n<br />\n元朗721之後本應係最好時機但miss咗<br />\n唔該趁機會煲大呢次警黑聯合同宣傳民防隊<br />\n<br />\n2.機場罷工癱瘓機場<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">點解冇人講</span><br />\n<br />\n機場post一個熱門都冇，連登仔智力同黑社會睇齊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個係罷工有用最佳力證<br />\n之後和理非行動可以瞄準機場<br />\n機場班友又可以起帶頭作用<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">煲大佢！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b757a4465840dfbde4491cc380c9f20211a3b3d9","tid":1419521,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:42:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b48bd1dd879c14d6daa42d6e8e528ed358eb9428","tid":1419521,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:42:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7484b8f074a8b86e263e792578bcfcd85219021f","tid":1419521,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:42:46.000Z","msg":"連登仔打香城online打上腦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3693999f19982fa45ab2f048eef93a758a8339c2","tid":1419521,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:42:56.000Z","msg":"<im